just a little api client I whipped up for interacting with PAS
Poker Affiliate Solutions API v3

Requirements:

  * libopenssl-ruby (you prob have this)
  * rexml (prob. have this as well)

Get an Auth Token:
-----------------------
pas = Pas.new
pas.authtoken(123456)

Show Member Info:
-------------------
pas = Pas.new
pas.show_member(123456)

Get Member List (can take a while if your list is big ;)
-----------------------------
pas = Pas.new
pas.memberlist
